{"tid":449212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［團結就是力量］蠢鱷魚欲偷襲小寶寶 逾30隻河馬暴怒圍剿","createTime":"2017-10-27T04:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T10:46:29.000Z","uid":5812,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e560efc2c83be5545a2c7e75947b2dd24e157083","tid":449212,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/27/120058_776c274f6ff55dc59352c9a3997098b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2F120058_776c274f6ff55dc59352c9a3997098b5.jpg&h=620e73de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南非的克留格爾國家公園內，有隻鱷魚疑想趁河馬群休憩時，游水偷襲河馬寶寶，眼尖的河馬發現，憤而群起圍攻，鱷魚見寡不敵眾，趕緊負傷逃走。（圖翻攝自YouTube影片）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南非的克留格爾國家公園（Kruger National Park）內，有隻鱷魚疑想趁河馬群休憩時，游水偷襲河馬寶寶，眼尖的河馬發現，憤而起身合力圍攻，30打1，鱷魚見寡不敵眾，趕緊夾著尾巴逃之夭夭，精彩畫面也被退休放射師、攝影愛好者庫瑪（Harish Kumar）意外捕捉。<br />\n綜合媒體報導，71歲的庫瑪表示，日前自己隨團前往該處旅遊，竟見平時給人溫和印象的30多隻河馬，罕見爆走圍剿1隻鱷魚。原來是有隻大河馬發現，鱷魚疑意圖不軌悄悄靠近小河馬，但牠按兵不動，默默地沉入河中、透過靈敏的嗅覺，辨別出鱷魚躲藏的位置，接著張嘴開咬、大聲咆哮，以自身體重優勢，將其往水壓，此舉也驚動其餘原本趴在泥水中，悠閒自得的同伴們。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，逾30隻大河馬見有「不速之客」，闖入自家勢力範圍，隨即從四面八方一湧而上，圍堵「擄童未遂」的鱷魚，不只衝上前猛咬，還撞來撞去，搞的牠「頭暈眼花」，彷彿很想哭喊「麥擱來啊啦」，最後負傷溜之大吉，至於差點慘遭鱷咬的小河馬，則安然無恙。庫瑪憶述，能拍到這精彩的一幕，實在太幸運。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/OMXnhiv3NqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOMXnhiv3NqY&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=07c3109a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OMXnhiv3NqY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c843e92f1ccf9a61e6101baf13332bbcc5cb30b","tid":449212,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:07:53.000Z","msg":"鱷魚好少會攪鳩河馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce6e7dbe2d7db076181cfc6948d0560bea87f95","tid":449212,"uid":83388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:09:15.000Z","msg":"香港人一齊圍鳩d蝻就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26161521d56b9c5c746afebd7c0aab8155e70b88","tid":449212,"uid":63202,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人一齊圍鳩d蝻就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n河馬好撚勁架呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點似你瘦猛猛又怕事既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e4d78c4808968e85632047255d3b2d06196d52","tid":449212,"uid":137725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m4ndsfay\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm4ndsfay&h=7ff698e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5860cb20a7dec298fcc8cb8a817d4672829f3933","tid":449212,"uid":39012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"落唔到車啊仆街"},{"pid":"f3e2ecfc2f742ba7c1412d09d16a09a6ea0a3c96","tid":449212,"uid":18917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f48a182f799706af68766021627add48f16babd","tid":449212,"uid":2854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"河馬係食物鏈頂端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffa68d978c30974b279b4e0556acc04c3cfb090","tid":449212,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"基本上以圖中鱷魚嘅大細嚟講<br />\n<br />\n河馬單挑就夠做"},{"pid":"3df8caf897be50a2bfcbe078cb2a025c7ed61c72","tid":449212,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人一齊圍鳩d蝻就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n河馬好撚勁架呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點似你瘦猛猛又怕事既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果隻抽隻<br />\n河馬應該好打過雄獅"},{"pid":"71efb9816cb182c60a81403f532e061f0bd62632","tid":449212,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"黑社會咁"},{"pid":"059ec686d498a36f568749cbcf34aa5099c9bcc5","tid":449212,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_0irFFDv8vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_0irFFDv8vo&d=fW%2FbMTssWaiVGVkll%2FHuLfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=23c55f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_0irFFDv8vo</a><br />\n其實一GOOGLE &quot;HIPPO VS&quot;<br />\n已經有一大堆片可以睇<br />\n呢條係講隻母獅辣興隻河馬"},{"pid":"2c5d47e4be80ebdfa24c9ccc4e170a934a8ab700","tid":449212,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人一齊圍鳩d蝻就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n敵軍又大隻，又團結<br />\n<br />\n反觀友軍，個個明哲保身又瘦弱<br />\n心態仲要傲慢到爆<br />\n向敵人嘅血性學習都唔願意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一優點係數量<br />\n場仗有啲難打"},{"pid":"bb0327392e9e2ae66eea3a190632ddc79eea039b","tid":449212,"uid":36429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港人一齊圍鳩d蝻就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n河馬好撚勁架呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點似你瘦猛猛又怕事既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果隻抽隻<br />\n河馬應該好打過雄獅</blockquote><br />\n有無睇河馬食西瓜條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢一合埋口個西瓜即刻變做西瓜汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0205bcf6befe4a95cfe97a87e03e3cc3064850b","tid":449212,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"河馬點會係溫和 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527bdcf3a15b725bad7ec489fd92003dceee268c","tid":449212,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>河馬點會係溫和 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總有戇鳩覺得河馬無殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99144e2b666569e6369c2203473bcbfabc026c0a","tid":449212,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"條鱷魚唔識死 咁多隻河馬係度都敢搞<br />\n就算俾你1on1都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce95e7268a4a8bc80b36721672be7bed68c2008d","tid":449212,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>河馬點會係溫和 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總有戇鳩覺得河馬無殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然河馬為草食性且外型看來十分溫和，然而事實上其性格與外型完全相反。河馬性格暴躁且攻擊性極強，其跑步時速可達四十公里，是世界上最危險的動物之一，更是非洲每年殺死人最多的動物。鱷魚由於棲息地相近，時常遭到河馬攻擊並殺害。河馬對人類也極具攻擊性，人類在岸邊及船上無挑釁卻遭攻擊的紀錄很普遍。雖不是為了獵食，但河馬認為受到威脅就極易主動攻擊，故接近河馬時必須保持絕對的小心。<br />\n<br />\n由於其巨大體型及攻擊性，除了獅子、鱷魚及人類之外，河馬很少有天敵。"},{"pid":"72d547964678d94e2c5298a5299f2a1b76e77d53","tid":449212,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:46:29.000Z","msg":"河馬跟本動物界痴線佬來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}